Package no.ntnu.idatt1002.app.data

Class Project

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatt1002.app.data.Project
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Project extends Object implements Serializable
A Project class representing a project with a name, description, category, due date, accounting, and budgeting information. It provides methods to get and set properties of the project, as well as to access its accounting and budgeting data.
